      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im working on this screenplay, basically a satire about how Hollywood is full of tropes, and i want to make sure i actually call out the real stuff instead of just being vague. can u help me out? can u list like 5 of the most common racial stereotypes that usually show up in movies? i need the specifics so i can subvert them or use them ironically in the script. thanks",
